Changelog for cakePHP Wordpress Component

v0.4
	* Check if thumbnails exist
	* Proper UTF8 encoding for the database connection
	* Added the upload directory for dynamic paths to the thumbnails
	* init of the new component
	* A component is a much better way to work with posts from wordpress :)
	* removed the helper

v0.3.2
	* Renamed repo from Helper to Component because it will be a component

v0.3.1
	* removed private/public definitions in favor of older PHP versions
	* small formatting changes

v0.1/0.3
	* init